Show HN: I created a podcast with chat-GPT and elevenlabs AI voice
text:
I think it's so cool, but HN does not seem to care :-) (I posted already, not as a show HN).
The podcast is based on the top five shares of the day - the one that the system can scrape online. From the web content, chat gpt summurize and write the podcast, and then elevenlabs AI voice reads the line, befor the episode is published on this small site and on spotify.
So definitely cool.

title: Ask HN: Are you willing to contribute to OpenAI Evals?
text:
OpenAI announced "https://github.com/openai/evals" which is basically collecting high quality benchmarks from the community. Do you think this company deserves to get the collective effort of the community?

For a company that is on track to monopolize on AI, I am strongly against contributing any our effort OpenAI.

I plead that community will not contribute until the model is open.
